{"tid":1727902,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨正式統戰南區！候選人 羅霄 係河北省政協，仲係大陸官二代！","createTime":"2019-11-16T15:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T19:33:57.000Z","uid":57671,"like":122,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"4483d3dd363202b88dd5cf3b69b6637203d947f0","tid":1727902,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"1. 共產黨背景<br />\n<br />\n羅霄表面接受過西方教育，加上港大MBA畢業，仲做過投資銀行；呢個履歷表面上好似好中產，無得輸。實際上，佢係中共安排洗底、滲透入香港政壇嘅深紅官二代！<br />\n<br />\n羅霄係河北省現屆（第十二屆）政協委員，並同時擔任香港河北青年會第三屆理事會會長。呢個深紅及強勁嘅背景，難怪連南區區議會主席朱慶虹都要聽命下台，乖乖交出主席之位！<br />\n<br />\n參考連結：<br />\n1. 政協河北省第十二屆委員名單<br />\n<a href=\"http://he.people.com.cn/n2/2018/0119/c192235-31160860.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhe.people.com.cn%2Fn2%2F2018%2F0119%2Fc192235-31160860.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=39eefc77\" target=\"_blank\">http://he.people.com.cn/n2/2018/0119/c192235-31160860.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 羅霄身為河北省政協的訪問<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinanews.com/wap/detail/sp/sp/shipin/cns/2019/01-15/news8729385.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinanews.com%2Fwap%2Fdetail%2Fsp%2Fsp%2Fshipin%2Fcns%2F2019%2F01-15%2Fnews8729385.shtml&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=2a7417e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinanews.com/wap/detail/sp/sp/shipin/cns/2019/01-15/news8729385.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWrmSNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWrmSNJ.jpg&h=07054e83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ce0ff3803491e4d7f9fae8cdfa250c124cd4ba4","tid":1727902,"uid":57671,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"2. 家族背景<br />\n講到父母，佢父親羅重係內地商人，無乜特別；但羅母蕭聖立就巴閉囉。蕭聖立女士係上一屆河北省政協常委，今屆交棒畀囡囡世襲！蕭聖立本身係聖大控股主席，但同時亦積極為中共統戰部辦事，包括擔任兩岸和平發展聯合總會監事長，主要以政協常委身份參與香港及台灣統戰工作。統戰統到安排囡囡選南區區議會，係咪要開始統戰南區區議會，開始赤化我地嘅社區？<br />\n<br />\n參考連結：<br />\n1. 政協河北省第十一屆委員名單<br />\n<a href=\"http://cpc.people.com.cn/n/2013/0130/c87228-20371220.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpc.people.com.cn%2Fn%2F2013%2F0130%2Fc87228-20371220.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=d451f359\" target=\"_blank\">http://cpc.people.com.cn/n/2013/0130/c87228-20371220.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 蕭聖立與統戰部的密切關係（太多，未能盡錄）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com/culture/237147/2019/0126/240736.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com%2Fculture%2F237147%2F2019%2F0126%2F240736.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=c0a016b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com/culture/237147/2019/0126/240736.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wap.cnki.net/qikan-XYTT201609006.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwap.cnki.net%2Fqikan-XYTT201609006.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=11a315ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://wap.cnki.net/qikan-XYTT201609006.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anto58m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fanto58m.jpg&h=04c44ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNJ8xOn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNJ8xOn.jpg&h=164f2cbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9416df8d69c84348ebe88bf028e49c453b76dd9f","tid":1727902,"uid":57671,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"3. 虛報住址<br />\n羅霄自稱家住置富，但直至目前為止，她創立並持股的阿美星教育機構有限公司（Amazing Learners Limited），其股東住址是一個為於薄扶林摩星嶺的住宅單位，由其父親羅重及母親蕭聖立共同持有，而並非置富住址。佢虛報住址、欺騙選民，請大家齊齊舉報！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDEomHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDEomHb.jpg&h=66b8e348&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9ocZtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9ocZtS.jpg&h=41bba009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a43574783121780038cd74fbe448c8111f879b1